'' Flags accepted by SCREEN and SCREENRES
''
'' Usage examples:
''	SCREEN 14, 16,, GFX_FULLSCREEN
''	SCREEN 18, 32,, GFX_OPENGL OR GFX_STENCIL_BUFFER
''
